citations:
  citation-awoiaf-dontos-hollard:
    source: source-awoiaf
    properties:
      locator: "Dontos Hollard"
      accessed: "2026-03-15"
    notes: "Born 261-263 AC near Duskendale. Died first day of 300 AC in Blackwater Bay. House Hollard, Crownlands culture. Father: Steffon Hollard. Aliases: Dontos the Red, Florian, Dontos the Fool, Ser Fool. Last surviving member of House Hollard, spared as a child by Barristan Selmy's intercession after the Defiance of Duskendale."
